@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About - Travel Tracker</PageTitle>

<div class="container mt-4">
    <h1>About Travel Tracker</h1>
    
    <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h4 class="card-title">What is Travel Tracker?</h4>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Travel Tracker is a comprehensive web application designed to help you document, organize, and visualize 
                        your travels across the United States. Whether you're tracking visits to all 50 states, exploring 
                        national parks, or recording your favorite RV destinations, Travel Tracker provides the tools you need 
                        to preserve your travel memories and monitor your journey progress.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h4 class="card-title">Development Approach</h4>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        This application was developed using <strong>GitHub Copilot Agent mode</strong> and 
                        <strong>specification-driven development</strong>. This modern approach to software development 
                        leverages AI-assisted coding to transform detailed specifications into working code efficiently 
                        and accurately.
                    </p>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        By starting with clear, comprehensive specifications, the development process focused on delivering 
                        exactly what users need while maintaining high code quality and best practices. GitHub Copilot Agent 
                        mode enabled rapid iteration and refinement, allowing for quick responses to requirements changes 
                        and feature enhancements.
                    </p>
                    <p class="card-text mb-0">
                        The result is a modern, secure, and user-friendly application built with ASP.NET Core Blazor, 
                        Entity Framework Core, and integrated with Azure AD for authentication.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h4 class="card-title">Technologies Used</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>ASP.NET Core Blazor:</strong> Modern web framework for building interactive web UIs</li>
                        <li><strong>Entity Framework Core:</strong> Object-relational mapper for data access</li>
                        <li><strong>Azure AD Authentication:</strong> Secure identity and access management</li>
                        <li><strong>Bootstrap:</strong> Responsive UI framework</li>
                        <li><strong>SQL Database:</strong> Reliable data storage</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
